name: Tek Arena
tag_list: seo, google-analytics, mobile-analytics, search-engine-marketing, ppc, sem, website-development
overview:
Tek Arena offers a comprehensive solution to build, manage, track performance and optimize campaigns for websites, product promotions & indepth analytics and turn data to actionable insights.

Tek Arena follows a strict protocol of exercising ethical Search Engine Optimization practices for clients to ensure the growth is consistent and positive in the short & long run.

With it’s diverse online solutions Tek Arena is proactively involved in complete Google Analytics Solutions along with Pay per click management and Mobile Analytics to help app developers track performance metrics of their apps on multi platforms like IOS & Android (HTML5 coming soon) and optimize ROI.

With it’s certified personnel in analytics, social media management, and mobile based solutions. Tek Arena is constantly looking and developing broader skillsets to deliver and outperform clients challenges and requirements.

milestones.description: Today Tek Arena is proud to be the first Hootsuite partner in India and offer wider range of social media solutions for our clients.
milestones.source_description: Tek Arena becomes the 1st Social Media Agency in India to partner Hootsuite and deliver a broader social media offering
